##  Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/nova-chatbot.git
cd nova-chatbot
```

### 2. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Run the chatbot
```bash
python chatbot.py
```

