## ➕ Adding New Intents

Open `intents.json` and add a new intent block:

```json
{
  "tag": "your_intent",
  "patterns": [
    "trigger phrase one",
    "another example phrase"
  ],
  "responses": [
    "Response option one",
    "Response option two"
  ]
}
```

